When a player gifts you, Why doesn't it show us what that specific object was? 
Riot had it on last season, I believe. Would it be just a setting of mine turned off? or did y'all actually remove it? If y'all removed it, please add it back on. 
(My friends gifts me randomly and there are quite a few champions or skins, wards, etc that I wouldn't know what I had). Thanks{{champion:44}}
